The paper discusses the implementation of efficient downlink channel probing and uplink feedback in FDD massive MIMO systems, which involves signal processing, communication theory, and network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
